Prints the config object to STDOUT

Source: R/Config.R
show-tiledb_config-method.Rd

Prints the config object to STDOUT

# S4 method for tiledb_config
show(object)

Arguments

object

tiledb_config object

Examples

ctx <- tiledb_ctx(limitTileDBCores())
cfg <- tiledb_config()
show(cfg)
